title: PM to lay foundation-stone of projects in DI Khan today
content:
ISLAMABAD, Dec 26 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif will visit Dera Ismail Khan today, the PM Office said on Monday.
During his visit, the prime minister will lay the foundation-stone of various development projects for South Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, especially the Dera Ismail Khan Division.
The prime minister will also address an event.
